{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "648b5a6e417cc3fb48d67df4", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eba2"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "63134c746e7bc9b33248370c", "title": "JEE Main 2022 (29 Jul Shift 2)", "isVisible": true}], "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 2, "approximateTimeRequired": 150, "question": {"text": "Light enters from air into a given medium at an angle of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>45</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math> with interface of the air-medium surface. After refraction, the light ray is deviated through an angle of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>15</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math> from its original direction. The refractive index of the medium is :", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "uF1ip", "text": "<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>732</mn></math>", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "JgSSQ", "text": "<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>333</mn></math>", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}, {"id": "DEJIr", "text": "<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>414</mn></math>", "isCorrect": true, "image": null}, {"id": "25fZB", "text": "<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>732</mn></math>", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "<blockquote><p><img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/a73d57f8-045c-4725-beeb-ec54d9da6ddb-image.png\" style=\"width: 249px; height: 130px;\" /></p><p>Given here,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>45</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math></p><p>Deviation in light ray,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>D</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>r</mi></math>, here,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi></math>&nbsp;is refracted ray.</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mn>15</mn><mo>&#176;</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>45</mn><mo>-</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>&#8658;</mo><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>30</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math></p><p>Using Snell&#39;s law,</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi>sin</mi><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>sin</mi><mi>r</mi></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mn>1</mn><mi>sin</mi><mn>45</mn><mo>&#176;</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>&#956;</mi><mi>sin</mi><mn>30</mn><mo>&#176;</mo></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi>&#956;</mi><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math></p><p>Thus, the&nbsp;refractive index of the medium is&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>&#956;</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>414</mn></math></p></blockquote>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "questionLabels": [], "masterId": "MOGJMPYQ40283446", "source": "EM", "bucket": "Easy Ques (Board Level)", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "category": null, "microConcepts": [], "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f